summary: Reasons Why Dan Would Die In A Horror Movie
body:
Reasons Why Dan Would Die In A Horror Movie

Reason 1: Dan passes a guy who’s in a wheelchair and looks literally insane, he says “He doesn’t look very threatening” (11:40 Outlast)

Reason 2: Walks past a group of bad guys and explains himself as he passes (12:32 Outlast)

Reason 3: “What if this is the Slendertube?” Dan asks as he still waltzes right in (Around 5:20 Slenderman)

Reason 4: Phil says they shouldn’t go in the house, Dan ignored him and knocks on the door (8:52 Outlast 2)

Reason 5: Dan says, “Hello? Spooky man, hello?” (14:20 Outlast 2)

Reason 6: Dan literally just goes where he knows the villain is (8:30 P.T.)

Reason 7: Dan decides to stare at the eye he was warned not to stare at (16:00 FNAF 5)

Reason 8: Dan fully walks into an obvious trap (14:37 of Little Horrors)

Reason 9: Says the evil machine looks like a futuristic bath and he’d get in it (6:15 The Evil Within)

Reason 10: Willingly goes up to attic that mysterious person on the phone tells him too because they “didn’t sound evil” as if that automatically makes them trustworthy (Somewhere in the Resident Evil vid)

Reason 11: Grabs a fucking stick as his weapon (Friday The 13th video)

Reason 12: Grabs a fucking pillow as a weapon (Phil’s Why I Went To The Hospital video)
